      "(-0.9937, \"The shameful truth is we have no politician's with integrity! I don't care about anyone being very rich, but a country that doesn't invest in it's citizen's can't truly prosper! Give pensions to politician's but cap it at $100,000 considering their businesses & portfolio's earning them $1 million plus annually! Then the low and middle class earners are so over taxed be it for land tax or everything else including the air, that they refuse the responsibility to raise 2 future  taxpayers! Criticize past communist countries albeit even communism was started by the European Zionists to destroy Christianity, as much as anyone wants to but look at China since they ended communism the workers wages rose 130 fold  education academic  level same for the poorest as for the richest as all citizens prosper so does the country! Russia in war against US, NATO, EU &Ally countries & under tens of thousands of sanctions together with 1 third of the world, by the collective West which is the 2nd 3rd of the world, the rest under Western orchestrated wars, coups, civil, proxy wars killed mercilessly and starved, yet they have no homeless, all have a shelter 3 meals a day even if not lobster, education, medical benefits! While we in the West growing homeless like mushrooms after rain. US alone in 5 years from 5 million homeless up to 48 million ( I thought it was 30 million) was corrected  by US statistics that stated 20 million children going hungry daily, life expectancy dropped from 74 to 55 years, because over 60-es end their lives in droves, as they can't afford living costs & medicine! And sadly it's happening in every Western country!\")\n",
